text: Beautiful place to live in and raise a family. Caring for elderly and children is easy with a childcare centre and a senior day care centre. My only complains are that people here smoke everywhere and this area has no eatery. Got to cross the road for food.
Perfect neighbourhood, with close amenities around. The only concern is hard to get a slot in childcare because of many young families here
